title: YTD - Youtube Downloader 2.0
description:
YTD YouTube Video Downloader

YouTube Downloader allows you to download videos from YouTube to your android Phone/Tablets
Very easy to use and fast.


Features:

Search Videos in Keywords
Download Videos in Multiple Resolutions
Download in MP4, FLV, MPEG and Many more.
Download Youtube to MP3



HOW TO INSTALL

1. First enable installing unknown sources on your android phone/device by going to settings -> security - > Unknown Sources

2. Copy YTD youtube downloader APK file to your Phone's storage

3. On your phone/device, go to file manager and locate the APK file you just copied.

4. Tap and install

ENJOY
